Class PerformanceTestApplication

    • PerformanceTestApplication

  • public class PerformanceTestApplication
extends java.lang.Object
    PerformanceTestApplication takes in user's input generates random sequences of data as well as sorted sequences of data measures the time for inserting a random and sorted array into a red black tree measures the time for searching an item in the red black tree
